10. Nc3 $14) 7... Be7 ({Maybe} 7... d5 {should have been played.}) 8. d4 cxd4
9. cxd4 d5 10. e5 (10. exd5 exd5 {leads to a symmetrical pawn structure in
which we be only slightly better.}) 10... O-O 11. Nc3 Bd7 12. g3 {Preparing
