of concessions!} 1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 g6 4. O-O Bg7 5. Re1 Nf6 6. c3 O-O
7. h3 a6 8. Bxc6 dxc6 9. d4 cxd4 10. cxd4 Nd7 11. Nc3 h6 12. Be3 Kh7 13. Qb3 f5
