1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 e6 4. O-O Nd4 5. Nxd4 cxd4 6. d3 a6 (6... Qa5 7. Bc4
d5 $2 {How can White punish this move?} 8. exd5 exd5 9. Qe1+ $1 Qxe1 10. Rxe1+
Ne7 11. Bxd5 $18) 7. Ba4 b5 8. Bb3 Ne7 {Black wants to put his knight on c6 or
g6. However, since he can no longer play ...Nf6, Qh5 may come at any moment.}
9. Nd2 Nc6 10. a4 Rb8 11. axb5 axb5 12. f4 Be7 13. Qh5 $16 {The queen is very
annoying on h5.} g6 $6 14. Qh6 $18 f5 {Now Black's king will remain stuck in
the centre and he didn't manage to survive.} (14... Bf8 15. Qh3 Bg7 16. f5 $1
$18) 15. exf5 gxf5 16. Nf3 Bf6 17. Ne5 Qe7 18. Bd2 Bb7 19. Qh5+ Kf8 20. Rae1
Rg8 21. g3 Re8 22. Bd5 Nxe5 23. fxe5 Bxd5 24. exf6 Qxf6 25. Rxf5 Qxf5 26. Bh6+
1-0

