1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 e5 4. O-O Bd6 5. c3 Nge7 $2 (5... a6 $1) 6. d4 $1
cxd4 7. cxd4 exd4 8. Nxd4 O-O 9. Nf3 (9. Nc3 $1 $16 {/+/=}) 9... Bc5 10. Nc3 {
It is important to stop ...d7-d5.} (10. Bf4 d5 $1 $11) 10... a6 11. Be2 (11.
Ba4 $5 b5 12. Bb3 Na5 13. Bc2 $14) 11... b5 $6 (11... d6 12. Bf4 Be6 $14) 12.
Bg5 {Trying to provoke some weaknesses.} (12. Bf4 $16) 12... Bb7 (12... h6 13.
Bh4) 13. Nd5 Nb4 14. Rc1 Nbxd5 15. Rxc5 $16 Qb6 16. b4 Nf6 17. e5 Nfd5 18. Bxe7
Nxe7 19. Qxd7 Ng6 20. g3 Rad8 21. Qf5 h6 22. Rd1 Ne7 23. Qg4 Bd5 24. a3 Be6 25.
Qe4 Bf5 26. Qe3 Bh3 27. Nd4 Rfe8 28. g4 Nd5 29. Qxh3 Rxe5 30. Qf3 1-0

