15. Qxc3 e6 16. Bc1 Rfc8 17. Ba3 Bf8 18. Bxf8 (18. Bc5 {trading the bishops
for the dark square strategy!} Bxc5 19. dxc5 Qb4 20. Qe3 (20. Rac1 {is also
possible.}) 20... Kg7 21. Nd4 {stabilizing the position!} Qa5 (21... Qxc5 22.
Nxe6+ {wins the queen.}) 22. a3 Qc7 23. Qf4 Qe7 24. Rac1 Rc7 25. Re3 h6 26. h4
{Little by little a powerful will begin.}) 18... Kxf8 19. Rac1 Kg7 20. h4 Qb4
21. Qe3 Qe7 22. h5 h6 (22... Rc7 23. h6+ Kg8 24. Rc5 Rb6 25. Qg5 Qxg5 26. Nxg5
{White has complete domination.}) 23. Nh2 Qh4 24. hxg6 fxg6 25. Rc5 Rc7 26.
